channel.title: Septemberscape
channel.description:
Hey guys i wanted to sort of revive my first rsps experience. I played this server called septemberscape. It had like black h weens black party hat and some other customs. It also had hell lands or bad lands and a demon in the wildy that dropped rares. If anyone knows of this base please contact me.
It also had Sky armour
Probably from like 2010 or 2009 area.... Just curious if anyone knows anything :P was septemberscape.webs.com
